      <title>各州起诉特朗普政府因取消的研究补助金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/states-sue-trump-administration-over-canceled-research-grants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府由一群由民主党领导的州起诉，该州声称联邦政府正在非法取消研究赠款，以资助他们所说的批判性医学和科学进步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/states-sue-trump-administration-over-canceled-research-grants</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:16:29 GMT</pubDate>
